      p(style='text-align: center; color: var(--text-light); margin-bottom: 30px;')
        | Help your neighbors experience authentic home-cooked meals by sharing your specialties

      .form-row
        label(for='name') Dish Name:
        input(type='text', id='name', name='name', placeholder='e.g., Masala Dosa, Chicken Biryani', required)

        label(for='seller') Chef's Name:
        input(type='text', id='seller', name='seller', placeholder='Your name or kitchen name', required)

